All Implemented Interfaces:
com.percussion.design.objectstore.IPSBackEndMapping, IPSComponent, com.percussion.design.objectstore.IPSDocumentMapping, com.percussion.design.objectstore.IPSMutatableReplacementValue, IPSReplacementValue, Serializable, Cloneable
public class PSRelationshipProperty
extends com.percussion.design.objectstore.PSNamedReplacementValue

The PSRelationshipProperty class is used to define a replacement value as a relationship property. This replacement addresses the currently processed relationship. Use PSOriginatingRelationshipProperty to address relationship properties of the relationship that started the current request.
